OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FThe home secretary has said that long-
OL,7,Fterm settlement in the UK is a
OL,8,F"privilege, not a right", as she
OL,9,Fannounced plans to overhaul the legal
OL,10,Fmigration system.
OL,12,FSpeaking in the House of Commons on
OL,13,FThursday, Shabana Mahmood set out
OL,14,Fdetails to end automatic indefinite
OL,15,Fleave to remain status after five
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FIt comes just days after the home
OL,19,Fsecretary announced reforms to the
OL,20,Fasylum system.
