OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FThe plan for "earned" settlement and a
OL,7,Fdoubling of the wait time before being
OL,8,Feligible for long-term status was
OL,9,Ffirst announced under the government's
OL,10,Fimmigration white paper in May, and is
OL,11,Faimed at reducing the number of people
OL,12,Fcoming to the UK.
OL,14,FThe move comes as it is estimated that
OL,15,F1.6 million people will settle in the
OL,16,FUK between 2026 and 2030, Mahmood
OL,17,Fsaid, with a peak of 450,000 in 2028.
