OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FUnder the changes, migrants will be
OL,7,Fable to apply for indefinite leave to
OL,8,Fremain in the UK after 10 years,
OL,9,Finstead of five years currently.
OL,11,FConditions for settlement include
OL,12,Fhaving a clean criminal record,
OL,13,Fspeaking English to A-level standard,
OL,14,Fhaving no debt to the state and having
OL,15,Fmade sustained national insurance
OL,16,Fcontributions.
OL,18,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,19,Fannounced plans to overhaul the legal
OL,20,Fmigration system
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
