OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FBut the government launched a
OL,7,Fconsultation on Thursday, running
OL,8,Funtil February, on a range of
OL,9,Fconditions that would make migrants
OL,10,Fhave a shorter or longer wait time for
OL,11,Fsettled status.
OL,13,FProposals, which will be subject to a
OL,14,F12-week consultation, mean migrants
OL,15,Fwho are on benefits could face a 20-
OL,16,Fyear wait for settlement, while
OL,17,Fskilled workers and higher earners may
OL,18,Fbe fast-tracked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
