OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FThose arriving in the country
OL,7,Fillegally could have to wait up to 30
OL,8,Fyears for long-term residency in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FAnnouncing the plan, Mahmood said: "To
OL,12,Fsettle in this country forever is not
OL,13,Fa right but a privilege, and it must
OL,14,Fbe earned.
OL,16,F"Today, that is not the case."
OL,18,FThose who already have settled status
OL,19,Fwill not be affected by the changes.
