OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FShadow Home Secretary Chris Philp said
OL,7,Fhe supported much of Mahmood's
OL,8,Fstatement, but accused the government
OL,9,Fof "copying and pasting" Conservative
OL,10,Fpolicies.
OL,12,FHe said: "The idea of a ten-year route
OL,13,Fto (indefinite leave to remain) is
OL,14,Fsomething that we proposed in
OL,15,Famendments to the Government's Bill, I
OL,16,Fthink, around about nine months ago.
OL,18,F"The Labour Party inexplicably voted
OL,19,Fagainst those measures and now they've
OL,20,Fadopted them.
