OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,F"I am delighted to see the Home
OL,7,FSecretary has got out the copy-and-
OL,8,Fpaste function on her laptop and
OL,9,Fstarted copying and pasting
OL,10,FConservative policies."
OL,12,FHe also warned that transitional
OL,13,Farrangements could create loopholes
OL,14,Fand reiterated calls for a cap on
OL,15,Fmigration numbers.
