OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,FEnver Solomon, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FRefugee Council, said: "These
OL,8,Fproposals risk trapping people who
OL,9,Fhave fled war and persecution in three
OL,10,Fdecades of instability and stress at
OL,11,Fthe very moment they need certainty to
OL,12,Frebuild their lives.
OL,14,F"We see every day in our frontline
OL,15,Fservices how stability, and being able
OL,16,Fto live safely with family, helps
OL,17,Fpeople recover from trauma and begin
OL,18,Fto rebuild. It's what enables refugees
OL,19,Fto settle, learn English, find work
OL,20,Fand contribute fully to their new
OL,21,Fcommunities.
