OL,3,CHome secretary announces plans to
OL,4,Coverhaul legal migration policy
OL,6,F"But long waits for settlement and
OL,7,Frepeated reviews will only add very
OL,8,Fexpensive bureaucracy and keep people
OL,9,Fin limbo.
OL,11,F"If the government truly wants a
OL,12,Fsystem built on contribution and
OL,13,Fintegration, it must give refugees the
OL,14,Fstability they need and want to become
OL,15,Fproud Britons."
OL,17,FThe changes are expected to be rolled
OL,18,Fout from next April.
